Program: Outlook
Title: Mass Poisoning Feared at Schools in Chechnya
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbry6
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Mass poisoning or mass hysteria? The spread of illness among teachers and student at two schools in Chechnya. Volunteers studying marine life on the coral reef at Fiji. Protests in Kathmandu. Aids treatments in Zambia. Opinions on capital punishment in US. Presenter: Fredrick Dove.